    "panels": [
      {
        "text": "### Loops and Lyrics\n\nMost songs have lyrics that need to be played in a specific order, like the Verse of a song\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/41536b0a02f5e82793f483ed72b7071f-Slide24.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-practice-parallel-panels-85cb8c21-00f5-4adc-8211-2a5cc3b71962",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Loops and Lyrics\n\nYou can use loops to repeat a backing track underneath the lyrics\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/21b966df306ef90357b6098dcf66f4c4-Slide25.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-practice-parallel-panels-4a54cf96-402b-4b28-849b-39ce2108afa9",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Loops and Lyrics\n\nIf tracks have different lengths, they'll need different loops\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/4d4f38744fff9c3a8d49a14c2786e318-Slide26.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-practice-parallel-panels-c5e66c79-2ba5-48c1-b6d6-0bb3484683fe",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Loops and Lyrics\n\nIf they have the same length, you can play them together in the same loop\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/5b059c6b2f349a34130d5f86f74aea9f-Slide27.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-practice-parallel-panels-c124f868-dc69-4e9a-a2c9-992717c34f86",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "Key Takeaway: Use loops to create backing tracks for your lyrics. Use different loops when tracks have different lengths.\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/76c1e2fb6c3dd264a296f968d8372512-Slide28.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-practice-parallel-panels-3a2fda8a-40d8-4541-8e47-429e2d6bdf6a",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true,
        "typing": true
      }
